Package org.planit.output.adapter

Class TraditionalStaticAssignmentLinkOutputAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.planit.output.adapter.OutputAdapter
      • org.planit.output.adapter.LinkOutputAdapter
        • org.planit.output.adapter.TraditionalStaticAssignmentLinkOutputAdapter
  • public class TraditionalStaticAssignmentLinkOutputAdapter
extends LinkOutputAdapter
    Adapter providing access to the data of the TraditionalStaticAssignment class relevant for link outputs without exposing the internals of the traffic assignment class itself

    markr
